          <li><strong class="text-white">Never bet Tie</strong> regardless of payout</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">Manage your <a href="/glossary#bankroll" class="text-gold hover:text-gold-light underline">bankroll</a></strong> - set limits before you play</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">Take breaks</strong> - the house edge works over time</li>
        </ol>

